name: SubcutaneousRoute
title: Subcutaneous route
description: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent the route by which a medication is administered, in this case a subcutaneous route.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Medication. The intent of this data element is to identify the route by which a medication is administered, in this case a subcutaneous route. ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with identifying a subcutaneous route for giving a medication. These are SNOMED CT codes.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
